11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the J.D. McCarty
13 Center for Children with Developmental Disabilities from any monies
14 not otherwise appropriated from the Statewide Recovery Fund of the
15 State Treasury created in Section 255 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma
16 Statutes, the sum of Eight Hundred Thousand Dollars ($800,000.00) or
17 so much thereof as may be necessary to provide medical care for
18 children with developmental disabilities who are disproportionately
19 impacted by the pandemic. Such funds shall be utilized in a manner
20 consistent with the recommendations adopted by the Joint Committee
21 on Pandemic Relief Funding on May 12, 2025.
22 SECTION 2. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
23 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
